const size = {
    mobile: '400px',
    tablet: '768px',
    laptopS: '1023px',
    laptopM: '1239px',
    desktop: '1240px',
  }
  
  const theme = {
    mainColor: '#0055b8',
    subColor: '#0a4297',
    mobile: `(max-width): ${size.mobile}`,
    tablet: `(max-width: ${size.tablet})`,
    laptopS: `(max-width: ${size.laptopS})`,
    laptopM: `(max-width: ${size.laptopM})`,
    desktop: `(min-width: ${size.desktop})`,
  }
  
  export default theme
